---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="CAPS - Experience benevole" description="Experience benevole au sein de l'association CAPS.">
	<article class="pb-20 md:pb-28">
		<section class="relative isolate min-h-[58vh] md:min-h-[68vh] overflow-hidden">
			<img
				src="/images/hero_caps1.webp"
				alt="Hero CAPS"
				class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
				loading="eager"
			/>
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-4 right-6 z-20 text-right md:bottom-6 md:right-8">
				<p class="text-xs font-body text-white/20">
					Photo: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/splmo_7410/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white transition-colors">@splmo_7410</a>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="container relative z-10 flex min-h-[58vh] md:min-h-[68vh] flex-col justify-between px-6 pt-20 pb-8 md:pt-24 md:pb-12">
				<a
					href="/"
					class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 text-sm font-body uppercase tracking-wider text-white/90 hover:text-white transition-colors"
				>
					<svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
						<polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
					</svg>
					Retour
				</a>
				<div>
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/80 mb-3">Experience benevole</p>
					<h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white mb-3">CAPS</h1>
					<p class="font-body text-sm md:text-base text-white/90 max-w-xl">
						Engagement associatif, communication sensible et creations au service du collectif.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="container px-6 pt-14 md:pt-20 space-y-16 md:space-y-24">
			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] gap-10 items-start">
				<div class="order-2 lg:order-1 grid gap-5">
					<div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden border border-border bg-card shadow-sm">
						<div class="h-full w-full grid place-items-center p-8 text-center">
							<div>
								<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Image principale</p>
								<p class="font-body text-sm text-foreground/80">Ajouter ici une photo forte, un montage ou une capture de communication CAPS.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
						<div class="aspect-[1/1] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/50 p-4 flex items-end">
							<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">Placeholder visuel A</p>
						</div>
						<div class="aspect-[1/1] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/50 p-4 flex items-end">
							<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">Placeholder visuel B</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-muted-foreground mb-4">
						Experience benevole
					</p>
					<h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-foreground mb-6">
						CAPS
					</h2>
					<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-body leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mb-6">
					CAPS represente une autre facette de mon engagement: travailler sur la mise en valeur des actions, construire des contenus lisibles et participer a une communication plus sensible et plus humaine.
				</p>
				<p class="text-base font-body leading-relaxed text-foreground/85 max-w-2xl">
					Cette experience m'a aidee a affiner mon sens de la narration visuelle et a adapter mes creations a un cadre associatif.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Contexte</p>
					<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
						CAPS est une association a mission sociale. Sa communication doit être accessible, bienveillante et en phase avec les publics qu'elle accompagne.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Approche</p>
					<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
						Valorisations des actions, creation de contenus sensibles, supports informatifs et visuels inclusifs et touchants.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Valeur ajoutée</p>
					<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
						Communication plus humaine, meilleure lisibilite des actions et renforcement de l'image de CAPS comme acteur solidaire.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] gap-8 items-start">
				<div class="space-y-5">
					<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-background/60">
						<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Panneau editorial</p>
						<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
							Ici tu peux ajouter un long texte sur la production, la relation avec l'equipe et la facon dont tu as donne une identite visuelle a CAPS.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
						<div class="aspect-[4/3] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/50 grid place-items-center text-center p-4">
							<p class="text-sm font-body text-muted-foreground">Placeholder pour une citation, un extrait de brief ou une note d'intention.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="aspect-[4/3] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/50 grid place-items-center text-center p-4">
							<p class="text-sm font-body text-muted-foreground">Placeholder pour une capture de post, une affiche ou un visuel reseau social.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-5">
					<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
						<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Missions</p>
						<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
							Conception de contenus, soutien visuel et accompagnement de la communication de l'association.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
						<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Apprentissages</p>
						<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
							Organisation, sens du detail et adaptation des messages selon les publics et les supports.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
						<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Resultat</p>
						<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/85">
							Une experience qui renforce ma pratique du design au service de l'interet collectif.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Galerie 1</p>
					<div class="aspect-[4/3] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/40 grid place-items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">
						Photo / visuel
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Galerie 2</p>
					<div class="aspect-[4/3] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/40 grid place-items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">
						Photo / visuel
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Galerie 3</p>
					<div class="aspect-[4/3] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/40 grid place-items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">
						Photo / visuel
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-border bg-card/60">
					<p class="text-xs font-body uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground mb-3">Galerie 4</p>
					<div class="aspect-[4/3] border border-dashed border-border bg-card/40 grid place-items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">
						Photo / visuel
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
				<a href="/bde" class="text-sm font-body uppercase tracking-wider text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">
					Voir BDE
				</a>
				<a href="/#experiences-benevoles" class="text-sm font-body uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
					Retour aux experiences
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</article>
</BaseLayout>
